PrecisOrder fixing the remuneration and certain conditions of employment of CAROLINE LABRANCHE, full-time member and Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montréal Regional Office), for the period she is acting as Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division, effective June 4, 2024, until such time as she is no longer required to act as Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division.
